title: using AES encryption
extract: So 128 bit AES encryption is faster than AES 256 bit encryption. The keys used in AES encryption are the same keys used in AES decryption. When the same keys are used during both encryption and decryption, the algorithm is said to be symmetric.May 19, 2015
